data.title: Barbara Stanwyck divorces Frank Fay
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.; Photograph was edited for publication purposes.Photograph caption dated December 30, 1935 reads, "Barbara Stanwyck, beautiful screen star, is shown in court here today when she won a divorce in less than five minutes from Frank Fay, comedian. She testified she was unable to live with Fay or give her best work in the films because he harassed her."
